de.oaam.model.oaam.scenario

Interface ScenarioContainerA

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, OaamBaseElementA
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Scenario, Subscenario
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ScenarioContainerAImpl, ScenarioImpl, SubscenarioImpl

    public interface ScenarioContainerA
extends OaamBaseElementA
    A representation of the model object 'Container A'. An abstract base class for scenarios and subscenarios. A scenario is a global, timely or variant dependent definition of parameters. For instance along a flight mission.

    The following features are supported:

    • Parameters
    • Variants
    • Operation Modes
    • Subscenarios
    See Also:
    ScenarioPackage.getScenarioContainerA()
